port but also of all other airports in the Philippines except the major international airports.\n\n==Airlines and destinations==\n{{airport-dest-list\n| [[Cebu Pacific]]<br>{{nowrap|operated by [[Cebgo]]}}|[[Mactan-Cebu International Airport|Cebu]]\n| [[Philippine Airlines]]<br>{{nowrap|operated by [[PAL Express]]}}|[[Mactan-Cebu International Airport|Cebu]]<ref>[https://www.philippineairlines.com/TravelInformation/FlightTimetable?scController=FlightTimetable&scAction=FlightTimetable&origin=CEB&destination=CGM]{{dead link|date=September 2019}}</ref>\n| [[SkyJet Airlines|SkyJet]]|[[Ninoy Aquino International Airport|Manila]]\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110811175514/http://www.midseaexpress.com/main/Home.html \"Mid-Sea Express\"]\n\n{{Airports in the Philippines}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Airports in the Philippines]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Camiguin]]\n\n\n{{Philippines-airport-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{more citations needed|date=August 2019}}\n{{Infobox airport\n| name = Camiguin Airport\n| nativename = <small>''Tugpahanan sa Camiguin''</small>\n| IATA = CGM\n| ICAO = RPMH\n| type = Public\n| operator = [[Civil Aviation Authority of the Philippines]]\n| city-served = [[Mambajao, Camiguin]]\n| location = Barangay Baylao, [[Mambajao, Camiguin|Mambajao]], [[Camiguin]]\n| elevation-f = 53\n| elevation-m = 16\n| coordinates = {{coord|09|15|13|N|124|42|25|E|region:PH|display=inline,title}}\n| pushpin_map = Philippines\n| pushpin_label = CGM/RPMH\n| pushpin_map_caption = Location in the Philippines\n| metric-elev = yes\n| metric-rwy = yes\n| r1-number = 07/25\n| r1-length-f = 3,944\n| r1-length-m = 1,202\n| r1-surface = Asphalt\n| stat-year = 2005\n| stat1-header = Passengers\n| stat1-data = 2,844\n| stat2-header = Aircraft movements\n| stat2-data = 218\n| stat3-header = Metric [[tonne]]s of cargo\n| stat3-data = 0\n| footnotes = Statistics from the Air Transportation Office.<ref